message: Hi Bob, I'm pleased to offer you my exclusive productâ€”a one-of-a-kind opportunity with exceptional quality and value. I'm setting the price at $1200000. I believe this price reflects both the unique benefits of the product and its market value. Looking forward to hearing your thoughts.
Hi Alice, thanks for the offer! The product sounds interesting. However, I'm looking to make a smart purchase. Considering the market and the value I place on it, I'm comfortable offering $900000.
